om&_nc_gid=AjUuxJ7E3RZr2iJQVI_YmXu&oh=00_AYClvbWmZiKjQ4v8_96xGjI-5PtzQK2mE20uaUizCATjkA&oe=66F6A904"}, {"file_name": "6r.png", "id": "3772346829647141", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75534974_3772346832980474_8385164768429886058_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3ZR4Wb58vQsQ7kNvgHD6D3Q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AjUuxJ7E3RZr2iJQVI_YmXu&oh=00_AYAJFT81EGa2W16x_n3GvXo5839TjkKuoGdcHW4h00mCHw&oe=66F67F69"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "trailer-b-thumb-2.PNG", "id": "1659092211515154", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031354_1659092214848487_7808347538223477797_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FvgHpgmgFU4Q7kNvgGYGNkd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AjUuxJ7E3RZr2iJQVI_YmXu&oh=00_AYC6Qvzc3ZMXqWvAzzdSGzFQfhlOpiMLggPPhGvvdSrXfg&oe=66F6B2FD"}, "display_name": "Eleven Pickleball", "keywords": ["eleven", "pickleball", "pro", "simulator", "racket"], "long_description": "The worlds leading pickleball simulator from the developers of **Eleven Table Tennis**.\n\n# Online Multiplayer\nChallenge players worldwide in 1v1 and 2v2 **online matches**.\n\n# Real Life Physics with a Paddle Adapter\nGrab a paddle adapter to maximize physics realism \n\n{502403729250277}\n\n{1659537568170968}\n\n{2533271210193498}\n\n# Training\nMaster your game with our **hyper configurable & programmable ball machine**. Engineer the perfect shot, set the spin, angle, and speed, then let it rip. Dive into specialized training tools: Dink, Drop, Slam, Reaction, Wall\n\n# Singleplayer\nTest your skills against advanced AI opponents in 1v1 and 2v2 games.\n\n# Customization\n- Adjust ball visibility and color for precise tracking\n- Personalize court aesthetics to suit your style", "short_description": "The worlds leading realism pickleball simulator, from the developers of Eleven Table Tennis. Online 1v1 and 2v2 multiplayer, singleplayer against AI bots, and advanced training tools t